<h2>Brower Support</h2>

<p>Mettle allows you to <a href='/try'>compare 2 CSV files</a> using only your browser so you can work with confidential data you cannot send outside your company.  We think this is a good thing because it helps you do your job better without needing to worry about sending data over the internet or dealing with any paperwork.</p>

<p>Unfortunately, there is a downside that we had to use evolving technologies that only work in some browsers so there are some features that may not work.  Hopefully, this does not cause you too much of a problem but we thought it would be helpful to let you know what each brower allows you to do.</p>

