<p>Notably, Internet Explorer and Safari are not fully supported yet.  Please <%= link_to "let us know", feedback_path %> if this is causing you a problem.  We would love to help you find a solution.</p>

<h3>Technical Details</h3>

<p>We do not fully support Safari and IE because they have not implemented the HTML5 FileReader API yet.  You can find out more information on browser support for the FileReader API at <a href="http://caniuse.com/filereader">caniuse.com</a>.</p>




